<head>ELEPHANT</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">大象</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>INTENSELY BIG BEAST which HAS IVORY TEETH AND A LONG TRUNK.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The standard word for the elephant is xiàng 象, and there are no common near-synonyms.</p>
        </div>
<div type="modern-chinese-criteria">
